Date: Fri, 03 Mar 2006 00:18:20 +0900
From: Kenji Kaneshige <>
Subject: [PATCH 3/4] PCI legacy I/O port free driver (take4) - Make Intel e1000 driver legacy I/O port free
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
X-Mailing-List: linux-kernel@vger.kernel.org
X-Lkml-Link: https://lkml.org/lkml/2006/3/2/127

This patch makes Intel e1000 driver legacy I/O port free.
Signed-off-by: Kenji Kaneshige <kaneshige.kenji@jp.fujitsu.com>
